46mm

Find a Harbor Freight and spend the $50 on this:

http://www.harborfreight.com/21-piece-metric-3-4-quarter-inch-heavy-duty-socket-set-5494.html

It's one of the most useful "cheap tool sets" I've ever bought. The
ratchet and breaker bar handles can withstand a surprising amount of
force without bending when removing stubborn nuts.

